  - Book: 1 Corinthians
    Chapter:
      - 12
      - Verse: 13
Tags:
  - perennial philosophy
---
For by one Spirit are we all baptized into one body,
whether we be Jews or Gentiles,
whether we be bond or free;
and have been all made to drink into one Spirit.
